data.description: An Awe-Inspiring Extra, Wide, Lushly Landscaped Lakeside Lot with Panoramic Views of Green Spaces, Bridges & Lakes, are just Two of the Attributes that make this Extended Capri, Truly Unique! In RiverWalk, A 24 Hour Manned Gated Community in One of the Best Locations in Palm Beach County, 15-20 minutes to Everything including Palm Beach, the Ocean & Airport! This is Only the Beginning! The Lush Entry Leads to the Foyer with a Stunning Leaded Glass Door, Crown Molding, Decorative Trim & a Designer Chandelier that Opens to the Stunning 18 inch Glistening White Tile Floored(That is in all of the Principal Rooms of the Home) Great Room with Crown Molding, Extra High Hat Lighting & a Designer Ceiling Fan! The Tile Kitchen, the Hub for Everyday Living & Casual Entertaining, has Stunning Bullnose Granite Counter Tops with Unique Granite Accent Tiles & Ceramic Tile Backsplashes, Extra Decorative Lighting, Crown Molding, Additional Granite Shelves, a Newer Maytag Double Door Refrigerator, Kitchenaid Dishwasher & GE Microwave & a Ceramic Top Range! There is an Under the Counter Mounted Sink with a Designer Faucet & Pullout Drawers in the Cabinets, Plus the Pantry & a Breakfast Bar that Overlooks 30 Feet of Fantastic, Open Entertaining Space with the Same Beautiful White 18 inch Tile Floors that is currently being used as a 20 Foot Dining Room with an Exquisite Venetian Plaster Accent Wall, the Epitome of Luxury & Sophistication, with a Gorgeous Chandelier & a 12 Foot Family Room that has a Custom Designer Ceiling Fan & a Wall of Sliding Glass Doors, both Spaces have Breathtaking Custom Draperies & Upholstered Valances, that lead to a Fabulous Oversized 17x30 Roofed Screened Terrace with a Ceiling Fan, that Opens to a 10x30 Screened Patio, that overlook that Breathtaking Extra Wide Premium Lakeside Lot with Lush Tropical Gardens & those Views of the Azure Blue Lakes & Charming Bridges! The Secluded & Private Newer Custom Carpeted Master Suite with a Custom Designer Ceiling Fan, a Walk-in Closet with a Built-ins including a Dresser Plus a Dressing area with Another Closet & a Designer Wallpapered Private Bath with a Double Bowl Vanity, a Large Stall Shower & a Linen Closet! The Second Carpeted Bedroom with A Custom Designer Ceiling Fan, has A Huge Walk-in Coset with Built-ins & with the Closing of a Door is like another Private Suite with access to the Main Bath with a Built-in Tub & Shower with a Newer Brass Glass Shower Enclosure, a Vanity & a Linen Closet! The Convenient Designer Wallpapered Laundry room/Butlers Pantry has a Glass Block Window, Loads of Extra Cabinetry, a Laundry Sink & a Newer Maytag Full Size Washer & Dryer & leads to the Carpeted 2 Car Garage & a Wall of Custom Storage Cabinets! There are Hurricane Panels Throughout! The Rheem HVAC was Installed in June of 2019! There is a Designer Furniture Package Available which would make this a Turnkey Opportunity! Contact the Listing Agent for Details The 600 Acre Community is Incomparable having 200 Acres of Lakes, 12 miles of Pedestrian Walkways with Cobblestone Bridges, Park Benches & Street lamps! There is a Roving Security Patrol, an Exclusive 24 Cable Channel to find out what is going on & there is a lot! The Town Center, the Heart & Soul of the Community has All The Amenities including 3 Heated Swimming Pools (1 Lap Pool, 1 Adult & 1 Resort), 6 Har-Tru Lighted Tennis Courts, 4 Lighted Pickleball Courts with an onsite USPTA Pro on Staff & a Pro Shop, a Fitness Center, a Bocce Court, a Tot Lot, a Post Office, Plus the Acclaimed "Centanni Cafe", a Genuine Italian Restaurant in the Town Center, run by a Chef with over 23years Experience in Italian Cuisine with Outdoor & Indoor Dining overlooking 3 Lakes for your Dining Pleasure serving Lunch, Dinner & there will be Special Parties on Holidays too! There are also Takeout and Catering Services! These Service & Amenities are included in the HOA! Plus, the grounds of the property, front & back are taken care by the HOA Fee plus so is the Newly Upgraded X-finity Platform Comcast Cable & Internet Service! It is like Living in a 5 Star Resort, 365 days a year! Sit Back, Relax & Enjoy Living in the Ultimate Florida Lifestyle Community! You will never want to Leave! This Residence is Unbelievable! Words Still Can Not Adequately Describe the Beauty, Grace, the Level of Style & Taste that makes this a Unique Beautifully & Lovingly Maintained Gem! It is also On a One-Of-Kind Extra Wide Lush Lakefront Lot & Just One Lucky Buyer will have the Opportunity to call it Home!
